POEx-Inotify version 0.0200
==============================

POEx::Inotify implements a POE interface to the Inotify (inode notify)
subsystem in Linux 2.6.13 and later.  Inotify allows applications to be alerted
to any activity on a file or directory.  See http://inotify.aiken.cz/

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    POE
    POE::Session::PlainCall
    Linux::Inotify2

